comment: I watched a significant amount of the trial online. The number of lies Amber Heard told is incredulous not to mention the intentional malice & harm she caused by telling them. She has committed perjury in 3 different trials in 3 different countries plus intimidated her employer to take the blame for her wrongdoing in Australia. She lied about very serious matters but also small things such as never playing the guitar in her life. She played a singer in a movie where she plays the guitar. There is so much evidence out there that she fabricated abuse charges to get what she wanted from Mr Depp in her divorce. And the whole world heard the truth about who she is on those audio tapes. She not only lies, she is an abuser. She needs to be held accountable for her wrong doing & breaking so many laws. It sets a terrible precedent to let her get away with all her crimes.
